x^4-4x^3-4x^2+16x-8=0
\begin{align}x^4-4x^3-4x^2+16x-8 &= (x-1)^4 - 10(x-1)^2 + 1 \\ &= ((x-1)^2-5)^2-24 \end{align}
\rm\:g\:
\rm\:1\!-\!\sqrt{r}\, <\, 0\, <\, 1+\sqrt{r},\: 1\pm\sqrt{s},\:
\rm\ 2 + 2\,\sqrt{r}.
\rm\:f(x) =\, x^2 - 10\,x + 1\:
\rm\: 0 < 5 -2 \sqrt{6} < 1 < 5 + 2\sqrt{6}\:
\rm\:g\:
= 2 + 2\sqrt{5+2\sqrt{6}}\, =\, 2\,(1 + \sqrt{2} + \sqrt{3}).
